OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few early
OL,6,Fshowers in the west in the evening,
OL,7,Fotherwise dry and cold with clear
OL,8,Fspells. Becoming cloudy from the south
OL,9,Ftowards morning with chance of some
OL,10,Frain before dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FCloudy with rain spreading
OL,13,Fnorth, this wintry on the hills. Rain
OL,14,Fwill turn showery and heavy for a time
OL,15,Fin the afternoon. Some gales in the
OL,16,Fafternoon, perhaps severe later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
